title: may 17: the beginning of minecraft
description:
Today on 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about how the beloved video game Minecraft came to be. Afterwards, she talks about Tyler, the Creator’s first-ever number-one album in the U.S. Join this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
